{"tid":1562710,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集體移民?] 沈旭暉：建立香港人嘅虛擬社會，有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-09-12T06:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:13:56.000Z","uid":214261,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e075058412f7fd62f468793743fe8d440b9e51","tid":1562710,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:22:40.000Z","msg":"今日終於有時間聽沈旭暉個港台訪問<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/videos/664410920734802/?v=664410920734802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fvideos%2F664410920734802%2F%3Fv%3D664410920734802&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=999bed95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/videos/664410920734802/?v=664410920734802</a><br />\n主要都係解釋返美國《香港人權及民主法案》，有跟開嘅大概都知乜事 <br />\n（女主持啲問題都幾廢下，仲要分唔到「福地」同「腹地」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n反而亮點喺22分鐘左右<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">關於建立香港人嘅虛擬社會</span> 果 Part <br />\n沈生大概係話<br />\n科技／網絡／虛擬社群令香港人身份喺未來會不斷強化<br />\n正如今次運動唔止局限喺香港，而係 connect 到好多海外港人<br />\n就算揸乜護照都好，只要有香港人身份認同，都可以為香港出一分力 <br />\n咁憑住香港人身份，我哋都可以<strong>建立屬於香港人嘅虛擬社群</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最終令「香港」超越物理層面嘅土地</span> ？<br />\n___<br />\n又係時候推下post，集體移民研究組其實仲存唔存在？<br />\n仲有無人討論？<br />\n[集體移民研究組] 集思廣益可以移到至少5萬人，人均資金50萬以下的集體移民方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381637/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381637/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9362f95040ae8abc7c1a6a40295fe0561ff222cd","tid":1562710,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"645a269f689ca2d24b9982ec7a10d819af4dc414","tid":1562710,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"好似有得諗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46070726a041b0a432f3ab3c4dc3be04d24ce46","tid":1562710,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"Zegapain<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b306036ea1bf960a457332961d0a90d7b011014","tid":1562710,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46070726a041b0a432f3ab3c4dc3be04d24ce46","tid":1562710,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"Zegapain<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"仲有樂園追放<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c3b211191320c87ece92c1a9ab4dc2272e8e3f","tid":1562710,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"645a269f689ca2d24b9982ec7a10d819af4dc414","tid":1562710,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"好似有得諗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"其實一直都覺得有得諗<br />\n但連登嘅討論好似唔太成形<br />\n定已經有人研究緊但我唔知？？<br />\n<br />\n求